{"tid":2260270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［一日爆三單勁嘢］前學生動源成員被捕＋港康碼＋疑共黨背景做港大副校","createTime":"2020-10-27T12:44:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T17:18:41.000Z","uid":13586,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"c4ba0e4c96eeac8e35baa8fcde75e3937fdd226c","tid":2260270,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T12:44:02.000Z","msg":"一日三單大嘢，前學生動源成員被捕＋港康碼＋疑共黨背景做港大副校<br />\n問你死未！<br />\n<br />\n好嬲，嬲撚完，之後呢？定已經麻木咗？定錢國偉死咗好開心當打和？<br />\n<br />\n十二港人未返嚟，海外手足仲努力緊，你呢？國安法下仲可以做咩？<br />\n我相信仲可以比你而家可以做得更多。<br />\nTweeter，TVB，黃店，貼紙師，眾籌捐款⋯⋯仲有冇更多。<br />\n仲有冇更多⋯⋯<br />\n仲有冇更多⋯⋯<br />\n呢一年多大家都攰都辛苦，自己都好攰。<br />\n淨係仲想光復香港，雖然之前都有屌過lunch哥種種不是，但佢嘅毅力不得𣎴承認，到而家都仲努力緊，你呢？前幾日最最最冇成本，難聽講句掛機呃live人數嘅十二港人集會，30萬人，你喺度嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n心很累。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不要麻木，只求保持温度<br />\n<br />\n學生動源多名前成員警署報到期間被捕 鍾翰林往美領館尋庇護前被國安警拘捕<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201027/WYHMKEYFRNEY3I7NQ7ZGNRUXTE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201027%2FWYHMKEYFRNEY3I7NQ7ZGNRUXTE%2F&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDPjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=4aa21c8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201027%2FWYHMKEYFRNEY3I7NQ7ZGNRUXTE%2F&h=2f3974e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201027/WYHMKEYFRNEY3I7NQ7ZGNRUXTE/</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭：將修例賦權強制檢測 港康碼apps即將啟用<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1078425\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1078425&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDPjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=3a6ba4dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1078425&h=0b738604\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1078425</a><br />\n<br />\n消息：港大校委會通過申作軍及宮鵬副校長任命 (19:39)<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20201027/s00001/1603794181836/消息-港大校委會通過申作軍及宮鵬副校長任命\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mi